            p 9.1.2  if a petition for your bankruptcy is presented to any court or if you are unable to pay your debts to us as and when they fall due; 
            p 9.1.3  if you commit a breach of any of the provisions of the Terms that is not capable of remedy or in case of a breach of any of the provisions of the Code of Ethics and the Rules of Conduct; or 
            p 9.1.4 if you commit a breach of any of the provisions of the Terms, including the documents referenced to herein and fail to explain to our satisfaction or in case of breach capable of remedy, to remedy that breach within 30  days after receipt of a written notice from us. 
